data.description: Now is your chance to own a little piece of paradise! Country living outside of town but within a short distance to all your shopping needs. With 5.5 acres of land you will have plenty of room to bring all your animals. This home is set to go for your very own hobby farm. Included within the 3 parcels you will find a 24x24 workshop, tack sheds, barn, grazing pasture, chicken coop, a variety of apple trees, peach trees, apricot trees, concord grapes, black berries, logan berries and so much more! The home sits nestled and secluded within the mature trees on a Hud foundation with Fort Hall irrigation with old water rights and no CCR's. Come see for yourself the park-like yard and the peaceful out of town living. Call today for your private showing!
